<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>THE incantation put by lovely Bride<br />
Before the thumb of the Mother of God,<br />
On lint, on wort, on hemp,<br />
For worm, for venom, for teeth.</p>
<p>The worm that tortured me,<br />
In the teeth of my head,<br />
Hell hard by my teeth,<br />
The teeth of hell distressing me.</p>
<p>  *       *       *       *<br />
The teeth of hell close to me;<br />
As long as I myself shall last<br />
May my teeth last in my head.</p>
<p>VARIANTS--<br />
On lint, on comb, on agony.<br />
On sea, on ocean, on coast.<br />
On water, on lakes, on marshes.</p></td>
